            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Language learner</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">Game changer for learning Spanish through authentic content. Context is preserved perfectly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
